"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-paralympics-will-bayley-paris-bbc-amanda-abbington-zara-mcdermott-b2596273.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 321, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Will Bayleyinsists ongoing controversy surrounding Strictly Come Dancing has not been a distraction ahead of the Paralympics and would relish a spell in the jungle on his return fromParis.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 534, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The table tennis star tore knee ligaments during rehearsals for the 2019 edition of the celebrity dancing show and expects to endure the impact of the injury for the rest of his life.\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 719, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Father-of-two Bayley recently claimed there was \\\"no duty of care\\\" from producers of theBBCprogramme amid concerns raised about the treatment of contestants byAmanda Abbington,Zara McDermottand Laura Whitmore.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 929, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"score\": 0.999676427382778, \"rank\": 0.0003233358639352777, \"text\": \"Bayley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\"}, {\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zara_Carmichael\", \"score\": 0.999994731826753, \"rank\": 2.9671503387920683e-06, \"text\": \"Zara\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zara_Carmichael\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zara_Carmichael\"}, {\"begin\": 914, \"end\": 928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Whitmore\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Whitmore\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Whitmore\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Whitmore\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 36-year-old, who has arthrogryposis, a congenital disorder which affects all of his limbs, felt it was important to share his experiences.\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet he has not allowed fresh interest in the story to divert attention away from ambitions of reclaiming Paralympic gold during the coming weeks, while he remains open to another reality television appearance, specifically on ITV's I am a Celebrity\\u2026 Get Me Out of Here!\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1301, \"end\": 1304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\", \"score\": 0.9943022246600188, \"rank\": 0.002822978333743336, \"text\": \"ITV\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITV_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really enjoyed my time on Strictly, it was just the injury that happened and the problems after with my rehabilitation and getting back from it that I struggled with,\\\" Bayley, who was partnered with Janette Manrara, told the PA news agency.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1517, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"score\": 0.999676427382778, \"rank\": 0.0003233358639352777, \"text\": \"Bayley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\"}, {\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janette_Manrara\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Janette Manrara\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janette_Manrara\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Janette_Manrara\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That injury will stick with me for the rest of my life.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am going to have that when I am older so that causes a bit of anxiety because I have got quite a severe disability anyway, so it's just a bit of a worry as I get older with my children.\", \"from\": 1648, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But in terms of bringing up the problems, it's not been a distraction at all for me to talk about Strictly.\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1945, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's important to get my thoughts across because it could help people and that's what I have tried to do really.\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 2060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And if I can do that whilst I am in the limelight, that's a good thing, rather than to be scared to talk and be honest about things because that's how things do not get sorted.\\\"\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2240, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bayley topped the Paralympic podium in the class seven event at Rio 2016 but had to settle for silver at Tokyo 2020 after battling back from the serious injury, sustained jumping from a table.\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2242, \"end\": 2248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"score\": 0.999676427382778, \"rank\": 0.0003233358639352777, \"text\": \"Bayley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He heads to the French capital, where competition begins on August 29, as reigning world and European champion.\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2547, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2452, \"end\": 2458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.8855461612538833, \"rank\": 0.12664645237963024, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2529, \"end\": 2546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"score\": 0.8739753729636421, \"rank\": 0.14245102796811437, \"text\": \"European champion\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Figure_Skating_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked if he would subsequently consider another outing on mainstream TV following his ill-fated stint on Strictly, Bayley said: \\\"Oh, yeah, definitely.\", \"from\": 2549, \"to\": 2699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2664, \"end\": 2670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"score\": 0.999676427382778, \"rank\": 0.0003233358639352777, \"text\": \"Bayley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd love to go in the jungle.\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2729, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think I have got a better chance in the jungle than I do dancing because I can not dance!\", \"from\": 2731, \"to\": 2823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It would be more natural to me.\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It would be a dream to go on it because it's probably my favourite reality TV show.\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the one I have always watched since I was young.\", \"from\": 2942, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It'd be awesome.\", \"from\": 2996, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We will see what happens - I have got to try and win a gold first.\\\"\", \"from\": 3014, \"to\": 3082, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My mum was always scared of rats and I think that rubbed off on me.\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me that would be awful, a rat on my face or something like that  With I am a Celeb on his radar, Bayley, whose daughters Bella, six, and Grace, three, will be among his many supporters in Paris, required little time to think of his biggest fear.\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3253, \"end\": 3259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"score\": 0.999676427382778, \"rank\": 0.0003233358639352777, \"text\": \"Bayley\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_Roosevelt_Bayley\"}, {\"begin\": 3344, \"end\": 3349, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999973156264, \"rank\": 2.684592836413557e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Rats are my worst, just the long tails and stuff,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3463, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My mum was always scared of rats and I think that rubbed off on me.\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3533, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For me that would be awful, a rat on my face or something like that!\\\"\", \"from\": 3534, \"to\": 3603, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 3605, \"to\": 3741, \"entities\": []}]}"